<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="" class="Incertae sedis Basidiomycota" family="Pandanaceae" genus="Mycelium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Mycelium" order="Incertae sedis Basidiomycota" pageId="11" pageNumber="36" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="family">Pandanaceae</taxonomicName>
), 1 December 2016, S. Tibpromma PE58 (MFLU 18-0005, holotype); HKAS100855, paratype, ex-type living cultures, MFLUCC 17-0599 = KUMCC 17-0294.
</paragraph>
